##Burglish Demo Text Pad. 2008##

-Standalone client  (Remaking of Burglish TestArea)


To compile the application

Choose:
Program->Visual Studio 200X -> Visual Studio 200X Command Prompt

At command line
C:\<project dir>\> nmake

To run
C:\<project dir>\> blg_textpad.exe

